Does anyone know what file(s) are incomplete?

English, Japanese, and Swedish dubs of the films are all complete.
English and Swedish dubs of the series are complete.

As of June 5th, 2012, the missing pieces are limited to:

Japanese episodes #40 and #199

Tracks 4 and 5 from the English Lunarock soundtrack.

Tracks 15 and 16 of the "Full Moon Collection" album.

Tracks 4 and 6 of the "Pretty Guardian Sailor Moon Soundtrack Collection"

The remaining 6 incomplete files appear to be JPG scans of the various parts of the album art from the "Pretty Guardian Sailor Moon Soundtrack Collection".
